From 7297551f91a11e21b8a7cd4e366fd2760b6181c5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mboa Dev <dev@mboa237.local>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 10:50:56 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(reviews): post-event reviews & ratings (#7)

- event_reviews table (1 review/user/event, rating 1-5, optional comment)
- EventReview model + EventReviewResource, StoreEventReviewRequest
- EventReviewController: public summary (cached) + list, authed CRUD
  Eligibility: confirmed registration + event ended + not already reviewed
- NewReviewNotification to organizer (queued, respects prefs)
- Event model reviews() relation; EventResource exposes reviews_count + average_rating
- Event listing + detail load review aggregates (cards show rating badge)
- Frontend reviews feature module: StarRating, ReviewSummary, ReviewForm,
  ReviewList, EventReviewsSection (summary, eligibility-aware CTA, paginate)
- EventDetailsPage renders the reviews section; i18n EN/FR (parity)
